'''Burnout''' is an article written by [[Morrie Mullins (real person)|Morrie Mullins]] as a tie in to the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] adventure [[Belted In: Incursion|''Incursion'']]. It was published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website on [[June 5]], [[2003]] and took the form of an anonymous interview describing [[Burnout (space station)|Burnout]], a space station that functions as a hive of criminal activity in the [[Thaereian system]]. The unidentified interviewee claimed it functioned with the knowledge of the [[Thaereian military|Thaereian Navy]]

